    <div class="m-case-study-section [ u-margin-left-3-dt u-margin-right-3-dt ]">
      <h2 class="m-case-study-section-title">
        Background
      </h2>
      <p class="m-case-study-section-blurb">
        Seniorlink works with states to empower caregivers with resources, information, and social support as they care
        for their loved ones. Seniorlink’s marketing team approached thoughtbot for a website redesign to better explain
        their value proposition to state agencies and service offerings to caregivers.
      </p>
      <div class="m-case-study-img m-case-study-img__center [ u-margin-top-3 ]">
